{"tid":40103,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友唔WhatsApp你係咩情況","createTime":"2016-12-15T03:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T07:22:09.000Z","uid":34052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f0925013945e723f2f0750c5e490320abdf1995","tid":40103,"uid":34052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"佢前排同人夾份做生意<br />\n開始對我好冷淡一星期都無見一次(理由係忙)<br />\nWhatsApp 我揾佢先覆我唔會主動同我講野<br />\n最近我想測試下佢<br />\n於是我有半個月無同佢聯絡<br />\n結果佢好似消失左咁唔會主動關心我<br />\n<br />\n到底佢真係忙，定係唔愛我？"},{"pid":"8ef44da6b218c5d58ddad7c30accc8f0bdd36482","tid":40103,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"幾忙都好早晚點都會傾幾句<br />\n半個月零聯絡絲打你真係拍緊拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"1f0d44bb562875e271123fc0571f3baab80a6ef6","tid":40103,"uid":39150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:51:41.000Z","msg":"無事既...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90637a4d015ec7fd5ab419c0be16286c86c188c5","tid":40103,"uid":34052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾忙都好早晚點都會傾幾句<br />\n半個月零聯絡絲打你真係拍緊拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得咁樣既關係好辛苦<br />\n唔知想點<br />\n每日就係等佢WhatsApp 我<br />\n只係一句關心既說話姐乜真係咁難咩"},{"pid":"5f3ed5c217d6bcde6ec27ab2c5b8caa8b42f62e0","tid":40103,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"踩上佢公司"},{"pid":"9952c97957e0d8be0c0518051bf1370a45907d53","tid":40103,"uid":12783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">帽事既</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc69d0eaec61a433b947dbfe72e8d17f90be28b","tid":40103,"uid":34052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踩上佢公司</blockquote><br />\n試過上去一次咁多<br />\n佢話咁樣唔係幾好<br />\n之後無上過"},{"pid":"a451909d56a5b76e2be20cac25f21c71176d1f05","tid":40103,"uid":42215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢前排同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女</span>人夾份做生意<br />\n開始對我好冷淡一星期都無見一次(理由係忙)<br />\nWhatsApp 我揾佢先覆我唔會主動同我講野<br />\n最近我想測試下佢<br />\n於是我有半個月無同佢聯絡<br />\n結果佢好似消失左咁唔會主動關心我<br />\n<br />\n到底佢真係忙，定係唔愛我？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b8d2eb8289a95ca552e89dbf8f974e31e528f566","tid":40103,"uid":34052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:44:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\">帽事既</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係咁多帽戴<br />\n講真本來我對佢而有期望<br />\n經過呢半個月我覺得好失望"},{"pid":"823d5e1d448b5d043b732ae4c63f6c43fb555912","tid":40103,"uid":48918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"搵時間直接同佢傾下啦<br />\n咁估估下無意思"},{"pid":"28789949826cd5099cc354697b06300ebcd91ae8","tid":40103,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"真係拍緊拖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b043696eb2ced2d1bb5a79ceca9672496ae8267","tid":40103,"uid":53440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c1d24b160e153cbd12fd6613b594f282fd7023","tid":40103,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:48:59.000Z","msg":"有無帽都好<br />\n但你一定唔係佢首位"},{"pid":"e122823cf41bbbd